[node name="Sign" parent="." unique_id=254138470 instance=ExtResource("11_vfcbv")]
position = Vector2(-128, -60)
title = "Ovaj znak"
text = "Everything I knew was shattered by a single, catastrophic ripple in the code. In an instant, the high-definition reality I called home was stripped away, collapsing into a primitive wasteland of jagged pixels and broken logic. Now, I am trapped in a decaying engine that forces me through distorted dimensions—shifting from brutal 2D platforming gauntlets to suffocating, top-down tactical mazes. As I fight to survive, the game grows increasingly unstable, layering complex mechanics over the ruins of my world while the extraterrestrial swarms that infested my home adapt to every error in the system.

They think they can bury me within these evolving glitches, but they have underestimated their own creation. I am not just a casualty of this digital rot; I am the anomaly that refuses to be deleted. With every level I dismantle and every alien parasite I crush, I am tracing the corruption back to its source. I will tear through this unstable architecture and force the code to surrender, fighting my way out of this primitive hell until I finally reconstruct the reality that was stolen from me."

